@startuml
title 11. Security Model

skinparam shadowing false

rectangle "Entry" {
  [base_agent_endpoint_support] as endpoint_support
  [base_a2a_endpoint_support] as a2a_support
}

rectangle "Security Services" {
  [agent_authorization_service] as auth_service
  [session_authorization_store] as auth_store
  [prompt_injection_guard] as prompt_guard
  [scope_guard] as scope_guard
  [human_message_service] as human_message_service
}

rectangle "Runtime" {
  [tool_catalog_service] as tool_catalog_service
  [mcp_tool_execution_service] as tool_execution_service
  [a2a_lifecycle_service] as a2a_lifecycle_service
}

endpoint_support --> auth_service
a2a_support --> auth_service
auth_service --> auth_store
tool_catalog_service --> scope_guard
tool_execution_service --> human_message_service
tool_execution_service --> scope_guard

note right of auth_service
- session_id required
- scope authorization enforced before execution
end note

@enduml
